OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA scattering
OL,6,Fof showers this evening, though soon
OL,7,Fclouding over in the southwest.
OL,8,FTurning wet and windy here by late
OL,9,Fevening, with rain moving
OL,10,Fnortheastwards across much of the UK
OL,11,Fovernight. Coastal gales developing in
OL,12,Fthe south. Rather mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FCloudy for most with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain, locally heavy at
OL,16,Ffirst. Becoming brighter from the west
OL,17,Fwith showers in the south. Windy, with
OL,18,Fcoastal gales in the southwest.
